{"tid":1683654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大三罷都搞唔成談何全民勇武","createTime":"2019-10-30T17:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T17:52:04.000Z","uid":100811,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d2584884b6f1ac33185dbcf4230bf03972d370e9","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"連登係到吹風全民勇武，咁多人有咁樣嘅思想準備，就唔會圍唔到狗救唔到人，唔會和理非走撚晒得返前線係到守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實香港人真係和理非底，但又唔想抗爭影響生活。每晚都只係識好嬲好嬲，但嬲完又正常生活。懲罰下黃店但如常返工。犧牲飯碗都不了，又點敢孭起法律責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n當年六四好撚快就罷市罷課，連百貨公司都有大字橫額聲援學生。全市都係支持學生嘅行動咁濟。今時今日香港，ig見到唔少人支持啦，但實際行動呢？無呀，嬲完咪正常返工返學囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">認真推多次大三罷，之後先諗全民勇武啦，而家三罷都未撚做到呀屌</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa46afdc3eb8653d344a30b9a77cb95ba8e8e8bc","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9f145a58d2a85cd27233ee7475eb777723e1ace2","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:21:07.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"73d7bd280e3ba3ebcde0520bc84cd5cf60f124d2","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:21:17.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"56760b8133a157f1e38c097b8f5bd91d6a0b60c1","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"57402d1f48943022d4a0015e248cd48e42d62a9c","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"85e38709c40b15af10fb2ebf8ea7a82a24af29e0","tid":1683654,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply